  <brief_title>SeriACL™ Device Trial for Anterior Cruciate Ligament (ACL) Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center Open Study to Evaluate the SeriACL™ Device for Primary Anterior Cruciate Ligament Repair</official_title>
